github 源码安装      https://github.com/openethereum/parity-ethereum
yum install -y gcc g++ pkg-config file make  clang  gcc-c++ 
安装比较新的cmake
wget -c https://github.com/Kitware/CMake/releases/download/v3.17.0-rc3/cmake-3.17.0-rc3.tar.gz
tar zxvf cmake-3.17.0-rc3.tar.gz
cd cmake-3.17.0-rc3
./bootstrap
gmake
gmake install

yum remove cmake
ln -s /usr/local/bin/cmake /usr/bin/cmake
cmake --version

安装
Perl
Yasm

curl https://sh.rustup.rs -sSf | sh

# download Parity Ethereum code
$ git clone https://github.com/paritytech/parity-ethereum
$ cd parity-ethereum

# build in release mode
$ cargo build --release --features final

清理
cargo clean
执行
bash <(curl https://get.parity.io -L)

常规启动
./target/release/parity
